skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: harry potter quotes
des:
Would you like random Harry Potter quotes? This skill will help you know some cool quotes and dialogues from the Harry Potter movies. Go on and ask one from alexa right now!
Please note that I am a Harry Potter fan and am publishing this skill as an individual, and am no way related to Harry Potter books publication houses, Harry Potter film production studios or J.K.Rowling.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
